{"id": "1282743157116764202", "channel_id": "1282575480083709983", "type": 19, "author_id": "1226317601831911467", "author_name": "tranquil_monkey_73179", "author_bot": false, "content": "啊原来是误会，抱歉我打一串字没加表情可能显得挺冲的🥲\n\n一起冲校猫，一致对外！🤪", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T16:43:20.872000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["777861907973406731"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1282731277895602196", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282575480083709983", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "建议取消主线礼包的时间限制", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1282723810323468298", "channel_id": "1282723810323468298", "type": 0, "author_id": "501758744175181825", "author_name": "inukami2266", "author_bot": false, "content": "如題，池太少了\n禮包一直賣，先不討論觀感好不好看、吃象好不好看\n石頭根本沒有地方消化，對營收也沒有幫助\n\n建議一個界域開一池 渾沌/血肉/深海/超維 各1\n\n然後各限定輪迴，各錯開一星期換角色也行\n算了一下現在各界域應該都有3限定以上了吧\n不論新/老手想玩什麼類型都可以試著捕啟靈or抽來玩看看\n尤其現在STEAM剛上不久，新玩家更多\n\"例如\"現在血肉核心就是羊媽，想要等羊媽池不知遙遙無期\n只想補啟靈又不知道要排幾個界域之後\n至於支線故事開不開無所謂，神父池都卡好幾週了\n想玩其他界域又不想抽一般池\n開了超限爆發系統就算想補命座每隻角色又不知道要等幾個月\n更不用說沉澱商店有更多東西要買\n\n所以這邊建議一個界域各開一池", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T15:26:28.237000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282723810323468298", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "池開太少了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1282831170865991680", "channel_id": "1282723810323468298", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "可是池子开得太频繁就不是限定了啊❓", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T22:33:04.985000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282723810323468298", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "池開太少了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1282850865979461813", "channel_id": "1282723810323468298", "type": 0, "author_id": "501758744175181825", "author_name": "inukami2266", "author_bot": false, "content": "還行ㄅ，出場後第 3 個月開始本來就有機會複刻，1年後常駐\n原本限定池就是這樣設計的，限定不抽就等三個月\n就算各界域全開 也各有限定的三隻可以撐", "timestamp": "2024-09-09T23:51:20.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1282850865870278748", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 161182, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1282723810323468298/1282850865870278748/image.png?ex=69cc5df8&is=69cb0c78&hm=a4774ceeb6366885055042a674ddcf8eb016e852cb27f22833658bed8b17d9af&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1282723810323468298", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "池開太少了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
